// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// UNLEASH INTEGRATION — Self-Hosted Open Source Feature Flags
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// Unleash (https://github.com/Unleash/unleash) is the most popular
// open-source feature flag platform. Self-host for free.
//
// Setup:
//   1. docker run -p 4242:4242 unleashorg/unleash-server
//   2. dotnet add package Unleash.Client
//   3. Uncomment this file and register in FeatureFlagConfiguration
//   4. Configure appsettings:
//      "FeatureFlags": {
//        "Provider": "unleash",
//        "UnleashApiUrl": "http://localhost:4242/api",
//        "UnleashApiToken": "default:development.your-token",
//        "UnleashAppName": "my-service",
//        "UnleashEnvironment": "development"
//      }

